item.title: About
item.dc:creator: kurtm83
item.content:encoded:
SERVICES

2D & 3D CADD services, specializing in set design/construction. rhino3d for all modeling, drafting, cnc layout, shop drawings/technical drawings and some rendering. complex rendering done with d5 render.

MY Story

over 10 years in the set building industry, including network tv, theater, fashion, trade show, retail and events, as well as many years of experience with cnc milling, 3d printing and laser cutting & engraving.
